    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Why They're Ailing</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Michael Hetsko letter on Eric Schmuckler's Dec 6 article holds television game shows are disappearing because they have become so stupid that no one wants to watch them (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Eric Schmuckler should be more blunt about at least one of the reasons that television game shows have largely disappeared [''For Game Shows, Fewer and Fewer Winners,'' Dec. 6]. That is, they've become so inane, mindless and, yes, stupid that no one wants to watch them anymore.</p>
        <p>MICHAE HETSKO  Milford, Conn.</p>
      </block>
